{"id": "43212", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=43212", "title": "Chamber of Sacrifice", "text": "The Chamber of Sacrifice is a &lt;a href=\"Shassar%20Sea\"&gt;Shassar Sea&lt;/a&gt; zone in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIn-game.\nThe Chamber is a large crypt located northeast of the &lt;a href=\"Oasis%20of%20No%20Return\"&gt;Oasis of No Return&lt;/a&gt; and north to the &lt;a href=\"Windswept%20Sands\"&gt;Windswept Sands&lt;/a&gt;. It is made up of 3 chambers. Each entrance leads to a separate chamber and there is a central chamber containing an inactive &lt;a href=\"Hell%20Portal\"&gt;Hell Portal&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt is on the bridge leading to the oasis entrance that &lt;a href=\"Valla\"&gt;Valla&lt;/a&gt; is ambushed by a &lt;a href=\"Magilla\"&gt;succubus&lt;/a&gt; and her &lt;a href=\"Ramesh\"&gt;thrall&lt;/a&gt;. It is in the central chamber where &lt;a href=\"Josen\"&gt;Josen&lt;/a&gt; is kidnapped by &lt;a href=\"Aeshama\"&gt;Aeshama&lt;/a&gt;."}
