{"id": "38683", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38683", "title": "Charged Bolts (Diablo IV)", "text": "Charged Bolts\u00a0are a Destruction Lightning spell used by\u00a0\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", a remake of the classic spell.\nIn-game.\nSimilar to previous incarnations of the spell, Charged Bolts allow spamming inaccurate, short ranged sparks that are most effective against dense crowds of lesser foes. They have the lowest Mana cost of all Destruction spells (along with &lt;a href=\"Ice%20Shards\"&gt;Ice Shards&lt;/a&gt;), but may hit the same enemy with more than one spark if their hitbox is large enough."}
