{"id": "4224", "revid": "1687225", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4224", "title": "Charged Strike", "text": "Charged Strike is an &lt;a href=\"Amazon\"&gt;Amazon&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Skill\"&gt;Skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\n\"An Amazon devoted to the path of Zerae will be able to harness the forces of vengeance and storms. During Rites of Vengeance, Zerae will confer to the Amazon attacks that unleash a wild burst of electrical energy, striking down nearby enemies. A grizzled veteran of the Time of Troubles once said: \"Spear-women walking the 'Path of Zerae' are best given wide berth, for they can be as violent and indiscriminant as the storms on the Twin Seas\". \"\nGeneral Information.\nSynergies.\nA lightning attack that releases charged bolts upon impact (not upon cast). It affects melee hits only, but applies to both Javelins and Spears.\nMultiple Charged Bolts are released (similar to the &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Charged%20Bolt%20%28Diablo%20II%29\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;), and since this skill is melee hit, the target is almost guaranteed to absorb one or more of these bolts, making this one of the most damaging skills in the game against single targets, especially larger ones (such as act bosses, for example). \nAny extra bolts that do not hit the target still fly forward and possibly hit enemies behind it. Charged Strike is very powerful by itself but also benefits greatly from synergies. These attributes make Charged Strike one of the most popular melee skills utilized by &lt;a href=\"Javazon\"&gt;Javazon&lt;/a&gt;s."}
{"id": "16756", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16756", "title": "Charged Strike (magic suffix)", "text": "Charged Strike is a &lt;a href=\"suffix\"&gt;suffix&lt;/a&gt; that can appear on &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;. It provides &lt;a href=\"Charged%20item\"&gt;charges&lt;/a&gt; of the skill &lt;a href=\"Charged%20Strike\"&gt;Charged Strike&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt can start spawning on items at &lt;a href=\"Item%20Level\"&gt;Item Level&lt;/a&gt; 33, but will not be able to spawn on all items until level 68.\nStats.\n\"Can appear on:\" &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;\n\"Is available on:\" &lt;a href=\"Amazon%20Weapons\"&gt;Amazon Spears&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Spears\"&gt;Spears&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gloves\"&gt;Gloves&lt;/a&gt;"}
