{"id": "5811", "revid": "21257", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5811", "title": "Cleglaw's Brace", "text": "Cleglaw's Brace is an &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;item set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nThe set does have some downsides. &lt;a href=\"Cleglaw%27s%20Claw\"&gt;The shield&lt;/a&gt; is pretty unremarkable and &lt;a href=\"Cleglaw%27s%20Tooth\"&gt;the weapon&lt;/a&gt;, despite having an inherent 50% &lt;a href=\"Deadly%20Strike\"&gt;Deadly Strike&lt;/a&gt; modifier, still has the potential for low damage.\u00a0Its &lt;a href=\"Attack%20Rating\"&gt;Attack Rating&lt;/a&gt; bonus tends to be pretty moot around &lt;a href=\"Lord%20of%20Destruction%20%28Act%29\"&gt;Act 5&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"difficulty\"&gt;difficulty&lt;/a&gt;.\u00a0The &lt;a href=\"knockback\"&gt;knockback&lt;/a&gt; modifier on &lt;a href=\"Cleglaw%27s%20Pincers\"&gt;the gloves&lt;/a&gt; can be quite annoying if an opponent isn't close to a wall.\nOn the other hand, the full set grants 35% chance of &lt;a href=\"Crushing%20Blow\"&gt;Crushing Blow&lt;/a&gt;, a useful modifier for boss fights. The 6% mana leech is helpful in keeping skill use more constant. The inherent 25% slowdown is helpful, and if an opponent is near a wall, the knockback modifier will make them unable to attack while the wearer deals damage with impunity.\nSet.\n (2 Items)"}
{"id": "5836", "revid": "233389", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5836", "title": "Cleglaw's Claw", "text": "Cleglaw's Claw is a &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". It is one of the three pieces of the &lt;a href=\"Cleglaw%27s%20Brace\"&gt;Cleglaw's Brace&lt;/a&gt; item set.\nAs the set is rather low level it won't see use much. But the poison reduction effect is potent and useful in boss fights with heavy poison damage, such as &lt;a href=\"Andariel\"&gt;Andariel&lt;/a&gt;.\nStats.\nDefense: \nChance to Block: Pal: , Ama/Asn/Bar: , Dru/Nec/Sor: \nDurability: 16\nRequired Strength: 22\nRequired Level: 4\n (2 items)"}
