{"id": "4719", "revid": "21257", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4719", "title": "Cleglaw's Tooth", "text": "Cleglaw's Tooth is a &lt;a href=\"Set%20Items\"&gt;set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". It is one of the three pieces of the &lt;a href=\"Cleglaw%27s%20Brace\"&gt;Cleglaw's Brace&lt;/a&gt; item set.\nCleglaw's Tooth has a wide damage range and pretty stiff stat requirements for a low level item, so a player may find themselves doing poor damage and having to wait until level 9-10 before being able to utilize it. On the other hand, it has a damage bonus that increases with level and a capability of Deadly Strike. Add the level dependent maximum damage for having an extra piece, and it is quite a viable weapon for early game once it can be equipped.\nStats.\nOne-Hand Damage: 3 to 19\nSword Class - Fast Attack Speed (-10)\nDurability: 44\nRequired Dexterity: 39\nRequired Strength: 55\nRequired Level: 4\n (2 items)"}
