{"id": "50470", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50470", "title": "Ferdinan", "text": "Ferdinan is an &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;, and close friends with &lt;a href=\"Valstus\"&gt;Valstus&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nAround &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231271\"&gt;1271&lt;/a&gt;, Ferdinan and his &lt;a href=\"warband\"&gt;warband&lt;/a&gt; went on an expedition, looking for a prize in north &lt;a href=\"Duncraig\"&gt;Duncraig&lt;/a&gt;. They found their prize \u2014 &lt;a href=\"Castle%20Cyrangar\"&gt;Castle Cyrangar&lt;/a&gt;. In the &lt;a href=\"Cyrangar%20Outer%20Hall\"&gt;outer hall&lt;/a&gt;, they were infected by a ravening haze that drove them to madness, then death.\nFerdinan was able to escape and return to &lt;a href=\"Valstus\"&gt;Valstus&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20%28City%29\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt;. There he was overcome by the haze, and began spewing more haze which infected nearby citizens and drove them berserk. Luckily, Valstus and an adventure were able to pacify the ravening citizens. Before Ferdinan died, he told Valstus about his failed expedition and gave him a map to Cyrangar.\nIn-game.\nFerdinan is an &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;.\" He is featured in the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; \"\"&lt;a href=\"Ruined%20Expedition\"&gt;Ruined Expedition&lt;/a&gt;\"\"."}
