{"id": "53012", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=53012", "title": "Festival of the Ancient Moon", "text": "Festival of the Ancient Moon is an upcoming \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\" event. It will run from September 13\u2013September 27, 2024.\nLore.\nThe Festival of the Ancient Moon occurs in late autumn\u2014after the harvest and &lt;a href=\"Mid-Autumn%20Festival\"&gt;Mid-Autumn Festival&lt;/a&gt;, and before the onset of winter.\nGameplay.\nDuring the event, players can earn Aspirant's Keys by completing daily tasks. Daily and weekly tasks can be completed to return rewards. Daily tasks include playing through &lt;a href=\"Iben%20Fahd%27s%20Sanctum\"&gt;Iben Fahd's Sanctum&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Castle%20Erebban\"&gt;Castle Erebban&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=\"Abyssal%20Verge\"&gt;Abyssal Verge&lt;/a&gt; to earn Runes, Moonrite Flora, Aspirant\u2019s Keys, and more. Weekly Tasks include levelling Runes, participating in the &lt;a href=\"Rite%20of%20Cleansing\"&gt;Rite of Cleansing&lt;/a&gt;, and more, to earn Telluric Pearls, Set Items, Legendary Items, and more.\nKey milestones within the event will earn you Rare Crests, Moonrite Flora, Runes, and a Legendary Crest."}
