{"id": "37633", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=37633", "title": "Fetish Village", "text": "The Fetish Village is a &lt;a href=\"Fetish\"&gt;Fetish&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"towns\"&gt;settlement&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Bilefen\"&gt;Bilefen&lt;/a&gt;, located in (or bordering) the &lt;a href=\"Deathmire\"&gt;Deathmire&lt;/a&gt;. \nLore.\nThe Fetish of the village were known to the people of &lt;a href=\"Port%20Justinian\"&gt;Port Justinian&lt;/a&gt;. It was said that no-one saw the &lt;a href=\"Fetish%20Patriarch\"&gt;chieftain&lt;/a&gt; and lived.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, the Fetish attacked Port Justinian, and brought their captives back to their village. The Fetish slaughtered a number of their captives, and impaled them on stakes, while took others to the &lt;a href=\"Kikuras%20Rapids\"&gt;Kikuras Rapids&lt;/a&gt; for an unknown purpose. Only a handful of survivors were left when they were rescued by a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt;, the Fetish remaining in the village being killed. The hero(es) instructed &lt;a href=\"Geli\"&gt;Geli&lt;/a&gt; to lead the survivors back to the port, while they headed after the chieftain.\nIn-game.\nThe village is encountered as a zone in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\"."}
