{"id": "38812", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=38812", "title": "Fierce Brawler", "text": "Fierce Brawler is a passive talent in the Berserker (Orange) tree.\nIn-game.\nThis talent works similarly to the \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\" &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20Master\"&gt;Weapons Master&lt;/a&gt; passive: it simply adds a bonus to the Barbarian depending on which weapons they \"currently\" are using. It only applies for the weapons currently used for the attack, not for the entire Arsenal, so it's not possible to gain both effects at once and likewise not possible to apply an effect to a skill with the wrong weapons set."}
