{"id": "26718", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26718", "title": "Finding the Forgotten", "text": "Finding the Forgotten is an &lt;a href=\"Event%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Event&lt;/a&gt; that takes place in &lt;a href=\"Act%20V%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act V&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It occurs in the &lt;a href=\"House%20of%20Corpses\"&gt;House of Corpses&lt;/a&gt;, a small building in &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20Heights\"&gt;Westmarch Heights&lt;/a&gt;. The building and the event always appear together or not at all.\nInside, several corpses are scattered around the building. A frightened and confused woman called &lt;a href=\"Lady%20Ansonia\"&gt;Lady Ansonia&lt;/a&gt; asks &lt;a href=\"the%20Nephalem\"&gt;the Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; to help find her precious pendant. After checking several corpses (which may drop items), she will find the pendant and recognize the bearer as herself. Furious and refusing to believe that she is dead, she sheds her mortal form and transforms into a &lt;a href=\"Unique%20Monsters\"&gt;unique&lt;/a&gt; ghost, then attacks. Killing her completes the event, awarding gold and experience."}
