{"id": "2967", "revid": "855465", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2967", "title": "Fire Ball", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Sorceress\"&gt;Sorceress&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Skill\"&gt;Skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\n\"Once she has learned the basic incantation of this spell, the Sorceress can collect a large amount of elemental fire and contain it within a globe of energy. Discharging it toward her enemy, those energies are released in a devastating explosion upon impact. This spell of mass destruction is ideal for bombarding the encampments of her enemies. \"\nGeneral Information.\nSynergies.\nFire Ball is one of the second-tier spells that the sorceress can learn. Though it is accessed relatively early, it can often be useful later in game as well.\nAn improved version of , Fire Ball sends a large globe of fire at an enemy, which explodes upon impact. The radius of the explosion is actually a total of 4 yards, while the tooltip states 1 yard, the missile code states that it has the same explosion radius of &lt;a href=\"Exploding%20Arrow\"&gt;Exploding Arrow&lt;/a&gt; with a damage radius of 4 yards.\nFire Ball benefits greatly from synergies. With maxed out synergies, Fire Ball is very competitive even in the end game in &lt;a href=\"Hell%20%28Difficulty%29\"&gt;Hell Difficulty&lt;/a&gt;, potentially doing 10,000+ damage per hit with the right equipment. While its damage per hit is lower than the likes of or , it is far more easily controlled and has no casting delay, allowing it to be spammed.\nSkill Progression.\nExplosion Radius: 1 yard on tooltip, damage radius of 4 yards in the missile code."}
{"id": "16801", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16801", "title": "Fire Ball (magic suffix)", "text": "Fire Ball is a &lt;a href=\"suffix\"&gt;suffix&lt;/a&gt; that can appear on &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;. It provides &lt;a href=\"Charged%20item\"&gt;charges&lt;/a&gt; of the skill &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Ball\"&gt;Fire Ball&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt can start spawning on items at &lt;a href=\"Item%20Level\"&gt;Item Level&lt;/a&gt; 18, but will not be able to spawn on all items until level 36.\nStats.\n\"Can appear on:\" &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;\n\"Is available on:\" &lt;a href=\"Orbs\"&gt;Orbs&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Spears\"&gt;Spears&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Staves\"&gt;Staves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Wands\"&gt;Wands&lt;/a&gt;"}
