{"id": "21303", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21303", "title": "Fire Brand", "text": "The Fire Brand is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Two-Handed%20Axes\"&gt;two-handed axe&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It may only be obtained through Crafting, and requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 60 to be used.\nIt has a level 70 version, also a crafted item: &lt;a href=\"Cinder%20Switch\"&gt;Cinder Switch&lt;/a&gt;. The fireball it launches deals 100% damage as &lt;a href=\"Fire\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt;.\nCrafting.\nThe Fire Brand can be crafted using the Plan: Fire Brand, 42000 &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt;, 15 &lt;a href=\"Reusable%20Parts\"&gt;Reusable Parts&lt;/a&gt;, 15 &lt;a href=\"Arcane%20Dust\"&gt;Arcane Dust&lt;/a&gt; and 20 &lt;a href=\"Veiled%20Crystal\"&gt;Veiled Crystal&lt;/a&gt;s."}
