{"id": "1460", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1460", "title": "Flavie", "text": "Flavie is a &lt;a href=\"Rogue\"&gt;Rogue&lt;/a&gt;, and member of the &lt;a href=\"Sisterhood%20of%20the%20Sightless%20Eye\"&gt;Sisterhood of the Sightless Eye&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nThe Sightless Eye.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231264\"&gt;1264&lt;/a&gt;, Flavie was stationed on the &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Moor\"&gt;Blood Moor&lt;/a&gt;. She cautioned a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20II\"&gt;group of heroes&lt;/a&gt; from entering the &lt;a href=\"Cold%20Plains\"&gt;Cold Plains&lt;/a&gt; before clearing out the &lt;a href=\"Den%20of%20Evil\"&gt;Den of Evil&lt;/a&gt;. Afterwards, she warned them to take care, warning them of the &lt;a href=\"Corrupted%20Rogue\"&gt;Corrupted Rogue&lt;/a&gt;s that dwelt ahead.\nThe Bloodsworn.\n&lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;Six years later&lt;/a&gt;, Flavie was with a group of Rogues led by &lt;a href=\"Kashya\"&gt;Kashya&lt;/a&gt;, intent on assassinating the leader of the &lt;a href=\"Bloodsworn\"&gt;Bloodsworn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lakrii\"&gt;Lakrii&lt;/a&gt;. The band aided a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;group&lt;/a&gt; outside the ruins of &lt;a href=\"Blackstone%20Village\"&gt;Blackstone Village&lt;/a&gt;, fending off the Bloodsworn attacking them. Apart from Kashya, Flavie and the other Rogues engaged in pursuit, but the Bloodsworn ambushed them, wounding many Rogues, and forcing them to retreat. Flavie reported to Kashya, who ordered her and the other Rogues to pull back to their battle camp, before ordering a &lt;a href=\"Classes%23Diabloi%20Immortal\"&gt;hero/group of heroes&lt;/a&gt; to pursue the Bloodsworn. Flavie gave them directions to their &lt;a href=\"Bloodsworn%20Den\"&gt;lair&lt;/a&gt;, warning the hero(es) not to underestimate their enemy. \nLater, Flavie and a group of Rogues led by Kashya assaulted the Bloodsworn's hideout at the &lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Tower\"&gt;Forgotten Tower&lt;/a&gt;. However, the Bloodsworn fought back ferociously, and Kashya ordered Flavie to hed back to the camp and ask &lt;a href=\"Akara\"&gt;Akara&lt;/a&gt; for aid. On the way back, she saw the same hero(es) she'd helped earlier at the &lt;a href=\"Tree%20of%20Inifuss\"&gt;Tree of Inifuss&lt;/a&gt;, along with &lt;a href=\"Hemlir\"&gt;Hemlir&lt;/a&gt;. However, she arrived too late to prevent Hemlir's &lt;a href=\"death\"&gt;death&lt;/a&gt;. She told the hero(es) about what was happening at the tower. They told her that as long as the &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Rose\"&gt;Blood Rose&lt;/a&gt; continued to exist, &lt;a href=\"the%20Countess\"&gt;the Countess&lt;/a&gt; (leader of the Bloodsworn) could not be slain. Flavie told the hero(es) to head to the creature, while she went back to the camp; she and Akara would join them at the Rose.\nIn-game.\nDiablo II.\nFlavie is encountered in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\". She is found at the junction between the &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Moor\"&gt;Blood Moor&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Cold%20Plains\"&gt;Cold Plains&lt;/a&gt;. Before completion of the &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;, she advises the player to stay in the &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Moor\"&gt;Blood Moor&lt;/a&gt;. After completion of the quest, she warns them about the dangers ahead.\nFlavie will attack any monsters close to her. She is not attackable and cannot die, so she is interesting to have around when fighting bosses (especially &lt;a href=\"Uber%20Diablo\"&gt;Uber Diablo&lt;/a&gt;).\nDiablo Immortal.\nFlavie is an NPC in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". She appears at the start of the \"\" quest, and the end of the quest. Her role in \"&lt;a href=\"The%20Horadric%20Bestiary\"&gt;The Horadric Bestiary&lt;/a&gt;\" quest was taken by &lt;a href=\"Isolde\"&gt;Isolde&lt;/a&gt; in the game's final version.\nFlavie also triggers the &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal%20Side%20Quests\"&gt;side quests&lt;/a&gt; \"&lt;a href=\"Beheaded\"&gt;Beheaded&lt;/a&gt;\", \"&lt;a href=\"Hijacked%20Supplies\"&gt;Hijacked Supplies&lt;/a&gt;\", and \"&lt;a href=\"Tough%20Vines\"&gt;Tough Vines&lt;/a&gt;\"."}
