{"id": "51189", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51189", "title": "Fleshcraft Hydra", "text": "The is an experiment of &lt;a href=\"Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;Zoltun Kulle&lt;/a&gt; that he locked in &lt;a href=\"Library%20of%20Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;his library&lt;/a&gt;.\nLore.\nA product of Zoltun Kulle's experimentation at its most deranged, this enormous construct lurks in the darkest pits of his library, crushing and devouring intruders. Any duty it once had to secure its ruined lair has been subsumed by insatiable hunger. C. &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, it was summoned using the lost pages of Kulle's grimoire and defeated by adventurers.\nIn-game.\nSummoning the is one of the possible outcomes of finding five of the lost pages during the &lt;a href=\"Library%20of%20Zoltun%20Kulle\"&gt;Library of Zoltun Kulle&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Zone%20Trial\"&gt;Zone Trial&lt;/a&gt; \"&lt;a href=\"Kulle%27s%20Hidden%20Chambers\"&gt;Kulle's Hidden Chambers&lt;/a&gt;\". Defeating it for the first time rewards the player with &lt;a href=\"Zoltun%20Kulle%27s%20Ingenuity\"&gt;Zoltun Kulle's Ingenuity&lt;/a&gt;."}
