{"id": "37671", "revid": "47915220", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=37671", "title": "Devil Kin Brute", "text": "Devil Kin Brutes are &lt;a href=\"Animals\"&gt;Animals&lt;/a&gt; found in \"\". It is found in &lt;a href=\"Demon%20Crypts\"&gt;Demon Crypts&lt;/a&gt; Level 1-2. They are only seen in the &lt;a href=\"Fallen%20One%20%28Diablo%20I%29\"&gt;Devil Kin&lt;/a&gt; variation unlike their smaller versions.\nThese Devil Kin-sized, melee bashers are not found where the smaller Fallen Ones are. They don't share their cowardice either, and will continue to press the attack regardless of the damage or deaths suffered by their compatriots. \nFunnily enough they know how to open doors unlike the smaller versions or at least have more strength in their arms to do so."}
